1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,316
Demon Bloodline... activated.

2
00:00:01,916 --> 00:00:04,756
Wait... this isn't my dorm.

3
00:00:05,156 --> 00:00:08,956
Coarse cloth, mildew, cobwebs... where am I?

4
00:00:09,356 --> 00:00:12,196
The face in the mirror... that isn't me.

5
00:00:12,796 --> 00:00:20,436
Lin Wan'er — a minister's daughter, made imperial consort, framed for witchcraft, cast into the cold palace. Three whole years.

6
00:00:20,836 --> 00:00:27,516
My lady! Madam Liu is here — on the Empress's orders, to send you to your death!

7
00:00:28,116 --> 00:00:29,636
Presenting Madam Liu—

8
00:00:30,036 --> 00:00:35,916
Consort Lin, the Empress is merciful — she grants you a whole corpse. You ought to be grateful.

9
00:00:36,316 --> 00:00:42,436
I can't fight them, begging is useless... Did I cross over just to die all over again?

10
00:00:42,836 --> 00:00:45,423
Host near death — Demon Bloodline, force-activating.

11
00:00:46,123 --> 00:00:48,003
Your... your eyes?!

12
00:00:48,403 --> 00:00:51,680
Minor demon "Madam Liu" slain. EXP +10. Demon Bloodline is now Level 1.

13
00:00:52,380 --> 00:00:56,380
From this day on, no one decides whether I live or die.

14
00:00:56,780 --> 00:01:02,540
Madam Liu... was a demon. So how many more are hiding in this cold palace?
